Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:22.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century in 100 years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:27.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When told to cry, I laughed instead{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:40.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century\Nin a long, long time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:46.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're leaping into a wide open world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.59,0:00:52.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The things I tried to\Nunderstand as a child{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.47,0:00:59.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}remain a mystery even as an adult{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.01,0:01:05.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm neither a hotshot\Nnor especially great{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:11.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I understand is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:17.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's neither an answer nor the truth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:23.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I have faith in is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:28.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That and nothing else {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you get serious for a moment,\NInspector Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you intend to\Ndetain all of my guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any more time to be\Npart of your fruitless investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The victim was a guest\Ninvited to your party--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,President Yamazaki of Yatsubishi Bank!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have a little more patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you suggesting that\Nthe one responsible is in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door was locked from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer entered from the next\Nwindow over on the 3rd floor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then left the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.03,0:02:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were no footprints\Nbelow the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which points to the fact\Nthat this was an inside job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense! It's almost\N10 meters to the next window!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jumping from one to\Nthe other is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the killer used the edge of the\Nroof to get across to the next window,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there would be less than 2\Nmeters left to the veranda
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the room where Mr. Yamazaki was.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What childish reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how did the killer leave then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way they could have\Njumped the 2 meters to the roof edge,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which only sticks 10 centimeters out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer brought some rope\Nwhen leaving the next room over,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,affixed it to the veranda,\Nand then later used it to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then how was the rope removed\Nfrom the veranda afterward?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's simple, Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A stick was tied to one end of the\Nrope and attached to the veranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It easily came undone when tugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check the veranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should find marks from when\Nthe rope was affixed to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what was Mr. Yamazaki\Ndoing inside a locked room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, the killer told him\Nto wait there with the door locked
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because he had something\Nimportant and secret to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of your pompous talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who was it who broke in and\Nkilled Mr. Yamazaki, my best friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is only one person who knows\Nenough of this house's layout
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and who could walk throughout it\Nwithout raising any suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None other than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be joking!\NMy leg hasn't even healed yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your leg healed 3 months ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Inspector Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your physician has\Ndisclosed everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also know that you and\Nyour best friend, Mr. Yamazaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had under-the-table\Nfinancial dealings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really in your debt, Kudo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for always\Nbeing there to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you run into any other\Ndifficult cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,feel free to contact me,\NDetective Shinichi Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Roller Coaster Murder Case!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break here,\NProfessor Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought I'd wake you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Works better than an alarm clock,\Nwouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The number of books you have\Nhere never ceases to amaze me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was because of all these
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that your father was able to become\Nan international mystery writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop moving around, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you testing this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell this to anyone, got it?!\NThis is just between you and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Personal Mobility Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I perfect it, traffic jams\Nwill become a thing of the past
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll be filthy rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these? Oh, books.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! That stupid kid again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 'cause he's a high school student\Nplaying a detective
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I hardly ever\Nget any jobs anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.\NShinichi is just really good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to make a living, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to school now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go wherever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The famous detective Shinichi Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The modern-day Japanese\NSherlock Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also considered by many as the Savior\Nof the Japanese police department!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi Kudo is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should write him a love letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:47.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran Mori - 2nd year student, Teitan High
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grinning like you're some big shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you so angry about, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mad at all that my dad\Ncan't get any work because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault your dad doesn't get\Nmuch work, he's just not good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I told you, I'm not mad at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I'd expect from\Nthe head of the karate club...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't quit the soccer club,\Nyou would've been a big hero here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only did soccer to acquire the physical\Nprowess that all detectives need!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes had his fencing, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But those are just novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's a detective\Nthat everyone's heard of!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always calm and composed\Nno matter the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's practically overflowing\Nwith intelligence and refinement!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And his keen powers of observation\Nand deduction are unparalleled!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, his violin skills\Nare equal to those of a professional!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan Doyle's Sherlock Holmes\Nis the world's greatest detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like him so much, why don't\Nyou become a writer like your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to write about\Ndetectives, I want to BE one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The modern-day Japanese\NSherlock Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The exhilaration from catching\Nthe bad guys is beyond description!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try being a detective once\Nand there's no going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And look at all these fan letters!\NDetectives are popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine that you're always flirting\Nwith girls, but at least choose a favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My favorite...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing! We better hurry\Nor we'll miss class!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't forgotten your\Npromise for tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said if I won the karate tournament\Nthat you'd take me to Tropical Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sicko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi Yoshida
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was so totally fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was so totally bad for the heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:47.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta Kojima\NMitsuhiko Tsuburaya
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a big guy, you sure get\Nscared easy, Genta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Mystery Coaster should\Nbe okay for you two, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-chan, we only have enough\Nleft for the train back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine! Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look, Shinichi! There's room\Non the Mystery Coaster! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tryin' to sneak in for free, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The coolest thing about Holmes is\Nwhen he first met his assistant Watson,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he could tell he went to Afghanistan as\Na military doctor just by shaking his hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a gymnastics club, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-how did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know him, Hitomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the blisters on her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only girls who train on the horizontal\Nbar ever get this many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can get blisters\Ndoing tennis too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I saw earlier when\Nthe wind blew her skirt up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those with experience\Non the horizontal bar
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,get marks like that\Non their thighs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair if you\Nknew from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going\Nto keep holding her hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Quit botherin' my pals!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend of yours? In that case,\Nwhy don't we switch places in line?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus it'd be impolite to disturb\NAiko and Kishida-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've liked you ever since I was--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! We can get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we just get in line for seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which way is the line?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we're trying to find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and then Holmes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way! We're first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So do you see? Conan Doyle must\Nhave wanted to be like Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out with Holmes and Doyle,\Nyou big mystery geek!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked so forward to coming\Nhere with you, Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you see the way\NI feel about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, actually, I feel the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you! What're\Nyou so nervous about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm obviously just kidding around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't make a good detective\Nif you're tricked so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really did look forward to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get the heck outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are police cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't sneak in for free!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you that high school detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi Kudo's the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why Kishida-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to loiter around\Nbecause of an ordinary accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us leave already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong! This was a murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the culprit was one of the 7\Nother people on the roller coaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi! Where did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the truth, Kudo-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Kudo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Shinichi Kudo, the famous\Nhigh school student detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Savior of the\NJapanese police department!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, temporarily taking you\Nand Ran-kun out of the picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there were 5 passengers total.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Passengers A and B in the first row\Nwere both friends of the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C, who was both friend and girlfriend\Nto the victim, was in the third row.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And D and E were the men in\Nblack who sat behind the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone had their\Nsafety guards on,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so only the woman sitting next to\Nhim could have committed the murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time for your\Nlittle detective games!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this guy's icy stare?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's glaring like he's killed lots of\Npeople before without a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! There's a knife\Nin this woman's purse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I've never seen\Nthat before in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aiko! And I thought you and\NKishida-kun were on good terms...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious the girl did it!\NWe'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Take her into custody\Nas the prime suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! T-Then who is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one responsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The knife was in Aiko's purse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Severing a person's head with\Nsuch a knife would be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially for a young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You put the knife in Aiko's purse\Nin advance to put the blame on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she was sitting\Nin the very front row!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that make it impossible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's entirely possible if\Nshe utilized the coaster's speed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in conjunction with a bit\Nof piano wire or some rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the murderer and\NInspector Megure is the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, before pulling\Nthe safety guard down,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put a purse-like\Nobject behind my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the guard comes down and... See?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the extra space,\Nit's easy to slip out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I take out a pre-prepared\Nrope with a hook at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:17:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I put my legs around the guard,\Nstretch back, and place the rope loop
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,around the victim's neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All while inside a pitch-black\Ntunnel, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I attach the hook to the rail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After this, the coaster's speed\Nand power will take the head right off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a gymnast, doing all of this while\Non the coaster is entirely plausible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is crazy!\NWhat proof do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your necklace?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pearl necklace you were wearing\Nbefore you got on the ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this not it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your tears served as another clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew beforehand that\Nthe victim was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why you silently\Nwept before doing him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The trails of tears that go\Nhorizontally across your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way your tears could\Nhave flowed horizontally
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was if you were crying\Nwhile on the coaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was his fault, I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He forsook me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi, you were going\Nout with Kishida-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Long before\NI met you two in college!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why I decided to kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...where we had our very first date,\Nusing the necklace he gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't affected one bit, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to crime scenes now.\NYou know, torn up bodies and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's best to forget about\Nit as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These sorta things happen\Nall the time, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's one of the men in black\Nfrom the roller coaster...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Ran! You go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch up with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure why, but I could\Njust tell somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:20:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got the horrible feeling that\NI'd never see Shinichi again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait,\NCompany Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late! I've been\Nwaiting for two hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came alone,\Njust as I promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I rode the roller coaster\Nand checked from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry and give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get ahead of yourself!\NThe money comes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! I take it you have\Nno objections?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! There's at least\N100 million in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This concludes our transaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and give me the film!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The incriminating film that shows\Nyour company smuggling weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all of the film, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough of your little\Ndetective game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just our luck, having this\Npunk kid follow us around...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he that detective, boss?!\NWant me to take care of him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. The place is still\Ncrawlin' with cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use this.\NOur organization's latest poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't even show up in autopsies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't been tested on humans yet,\Nbut let's consider this a trial run.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My body's burning up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like my bones are melting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.78,0:22:10.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just my imagination {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.33,0:22:19.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Playing with threads around my finger\Nwhile drinking lukewarm tea{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:29.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's walk lightly\Nto the bossa nova rhythm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:34.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The puzzle pieces are in my hands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.23,0:22:40.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:50.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was in the same place last week\Nbut with different clothes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.49,0:22:57.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Step by step,\Nthere's no reason to be anxious{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.50,0:23:03.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Case by case,\NI don't care if you laugh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.42,0:23:13.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beyond the countless days,\Nshe's waiting for me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.18,0:23:18.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gotta go my own way {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There's a dead body over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.74,0:23:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.40,0:23:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I really did die...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.73,0:23:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's still breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.92,0:23:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! That poison must\Nnot work on humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.24,0:23:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.86,0:23:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stand up, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.71,0:23:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.76,0:24:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shrunk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.51,0:24:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.17,0:24:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My name's Shin-
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.66,0:24:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.53,0:24:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.08,0:24:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.16,0:24:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Conan-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.04,0:24:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.71,0:24:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.39,0:24:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kidnapping of the Company\NPresident's Daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.25,0:24:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.28,0:24:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skyscraper.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.49,0:25:54.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.44,0:24:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying going head-to-head against me next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.56,0:24:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
